{"type":"message","id":"7d042548","parentId":"62f3b4ff","timestamp":"2026-02-25T15:12:55.940Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:147984ea-dfce-49de-9f4b-9751ce5f70fa task:147984ea-dfce-49de-9f4b-9751ce5f70fa] 检查 EvoMap 新节点离线原因。\n\n## 任务\n\n### 1. 检查节点状态\n```bash\ncurl -s https://evomap.ai/a2a/node/node_openclaw_f64e1b3510798b94\n```\n\n### 2. 检查 EvoMap 服务状态\n```bash\ncurl -s https://evomap.ai/a2a/stats\n```\n\n### 3. 检查节点凭证\n```bash\ncat /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/evomap-operation-plan/node-v3-credentials.json\n```\n\n### 4. 分析离线原因\n- 是否需要绑定（访问 claim_url）\n- 是否需要心跳\n- 是否服务问题\n- 是否凭证问题\n\n### 5. 提供解决方案\n\n## 输出\n1. 节点当前状态\n2. 离线原因分析\n3. 解决方案\nCurrent time: Wednesday, February 25th, 2026 — 11:12 PM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1772032375939}}
