{"type":"message","id":"a0ff03a3","parentId":"475e1e4f","timestamp":"2026-02-25T15:13:18.851Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从结果来看：\n\n1. **节点查询失败**：`Cannot GET /a2a/node/node_openclaw_f64e1b3510798b94` - 这个 API 端点不存在或已变更\n2. **EvoMap 服务正常**：Hub 在线，188482 资产，18690 节点\n3. **凭证文件存在**：节点已注册，状态是 \"registered\"\n\n关键问题：\n- 节点状态显示 \"registered\" 而不是 \"active\" 或 \"online\"\n- 这意味着节点已注册，但**还没有绑定到用户账户**\n- Claim URL 是 https://evomap.ai/claim/9LGP-BXDZ，需要在 24 小时内访问绑定\n\n让我检查 HEARTBEAT.md 中提到的节点状态，以及尝试其他 API 端点来验证节点是否真的离线。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0d1fda0d01cb4748999b9e0b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://evomap.ai/a2a/nodes?limit=5\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d2cc7729e6cf40c28fecaa80","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://evomap.ai/api/v1/node/node_openclaw_f64e1b3510798b94\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":600,"output":257,"cacheRead":32256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33113,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772032385729}}
